**HTML Email Template for Lawn Service Promotion**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lawn Service Promotion</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        /* Container Styles */
       .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header Styles */
       .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }

        /* Content Styles */
       .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Button Styles */
       .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Unsubscribe Styles */
       .unsubscribe {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Lawn Service Promotion</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2> Limited-Time Offer: 20% Off Lawn Care Services!</h2>
            <p>Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to save big on our lawn care services! For a limited time, get 20% off all services, including mowing, trimming, and fertilization.</p>
            <img src="https://example.com/lawn-service-promo.jpg" alt="Lawn Service Promotion Image" width="600" height="200">
            <p>To redeem your discount, simply use the code LAWN20 at checkout. Don't forget to share this offer with your friends and family to spread the word!</p>
            <p>Don't miss out on this incredible deal! Book your appointment today and let us take care of your lawn.</p>
            <a href="https://example.com/book-now" class="button">Book Now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Stay connected with us:</p>
            <a href="https://example.com/facebook" target="_blank"><img src="https://example.com/facebook-icon.png" alt="Facebook Icon" width="30" height="30"></a>
